      "path": "audio/narrations/rotating-calipers/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "也就是相距最远的那两个点，隔着多远的距离。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rotating-calipers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
